{"tid":441302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入稟覆核警察遊樂會大會　「長洲覆核王」申請被駁回　官指濫用司法程序","createTime":"2017-10-19T14:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T14:18:18.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3cfffb25a1f818eb58a6fd2e2c96bede0af92593","tid":441302,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入稟覆核警察遊樂會大會　「長洲覆核王」申請被駁回　官指濫用司法程序</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171019/s00001/062e791feaf9a50f26731a35aa8b497f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171019%2Fs00001%2F062e791feaf9a50f26731a35aa8b497f.jpg&h=95a862db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察員方組織今年2月在太子警察遊樂會舉行大會，聲援因在佔領時襲擊示威者而被判囚兩年的7名警員。「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅其後入稟高院，要求法庭宣告大會屬非法集會，高院法官早前聽取雙方陳辭後，隨即駁回申請，今日頒下裁決理由指郭的申請無疑會收緊法庭對公眾集會限制。雖相信郭沒有惡意，但他指郭是一個「多管閒事」的人，亦指郭在本案中未有足夠的利害關係，可被視為濫用司法程序。<br />\n<br />\n法官周家明在判辭中指，太子警察遊樂會毫無疑問是一棟私人物業，進入大廈人士必須出示有效身分證明。因此周官裁定當日集會絕非公眾集會，事前亦不須向警方申請不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n政府一方曾質疑郭在本案中沒有足夠利害關係，周官同意此說法，因郭並非警務人員，亦非警察遊樂會會員，故沒有證據顯示集會會對他造成不便。<br />\n<br />\n周官指，諷刺的是郭要求法庭釐清有關公眾集會條例，即要求法庭對香港公眾的集會施加更嚴苛限制，而非為他本人或其他人爭取更多的集會自由。因此，周官認為郭可被形容為一個「多管閒事」的人。周官亦指，郭未有足夠的利害關係提出是次訴訟，可被視為濫用司法程序，故下令郭須支付政府一方訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171019/s00001/1508403538447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171019%2Fs00001%2F1508403538447&d=LwSsvyZ8f9r1mutVEsvrM0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e9e43ad9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171019%2Fs00001%2F1508403538447&h=684ac640\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171019/s00001/1508403538447</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213b415bd2a158a1a8b2cbb869316bdff1bdb79c","tid":441302,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea44d33f00d758b69c9990acc75234928defaea","tid":441302,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:07:29.000Z","msg":"法治社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n警察集會都唔關公眾利益事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5cd01c81a51835852796054599e5e7eea9339c","tid":441302,"uid":98415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:11:59.000Z","msg":"私人地方 公眾集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ac073fed3d7fdf33cec312f55f6c93836d756b","tid":441302,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"多管閒事是英雄特質，要是人人只會各家自掃門前雪，咁社會就會變得冷漠"},{"pid":"123ad7c84f0636b916fd5e62ae47e415329f70eb","tid":441302,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多管閒事是英雄特質，要是人人只會各家自掃門前雪，咁社會就會變得冷漠</blockquote><br />\n法官是垃圾"},{"pid":"298e2fd40afce45b9acbd5551b54f5dadf7c68cb","tid":441302,"uid":98415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"突然諗到<br />\n同告 曹星如 公眾地方非法打鬥 有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}